Freescale's IoT Gateway BSP
===========================

To get the BSP you need to have `repo` installed. Install the `repo` utility:

$ mkdir ~/bin
$ curl https://dl-ssl.google.com/dl/googlesource/git-repo/repo > ~/bin/repo
$ chmod a+x ~/bin/repo
$ PATH=${PATH}:~/bin

Download the BSP source:

$ mkdir iotg
$ cd iotg
$ repo init -u git://sw-git.freescale.net/fsl-arm-yocto-bsp.git -b daisy-3.10.53-1.1.0_iotg [-m fido]
$ repo sync

The default BSP (i.e., no -m option) is for daisy.
